{"tid":1528050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]根本政府831恐襲就係引我地今日91阻路衝突做藉口清場，證明政府驚和理塞","createTime":"2019-09-01T12:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:54:20.000Z","uid":31511,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"06de7afde42235be876ea45048f6b81bd851c942","tid":1528050,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:26:28.000Z","msg":"如果今日完全stick to the plan, 淨係和理塞，雖然未必令到航班取消， 但起碼無藉口比狗屠城（我覺得）<br />\n<br />\n政府就係無方法對付和理塞， 所以琴晚配合黨鐵做大仆街， 令今日大家都添上一層怒火，做出計劃以外既野，令狗狗有藉口做野。<br />\n<br />\n唔係想分化，唔係想失敗主義，主旨係想講政府比大家想像中聰明，大家要冷靜見招拆招<br />\n<br />\n正評=認同，所以再搞多次 真。和你塞，完全合法版，忍忍手<br />\n負評=唔認同，收皮啦個19政府點都有藉口屠城架啦！今日大家無做錯到！"},{"pid":"75d0145e56ec68ee6db8d2e9a5301c668d22db79","tid":1528050,"uid":31511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"f09cc11561e60a97548f830172ffa3928c3d29c4","tid":1528050,"uid":31511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"如果今日完全守法， 個故事又會點發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6311adfa727d6844be0041152b3f96104093f822","tid":1528050,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"討論下"},{"pid":"dc59dcb8f53c40a4576e599bc545a6c10b903cd6","tid":1528050,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:37:29.000Z","msg":"例如破壞東涌閘機。。。<br />\n<br />\n今日做左，之後黨鐵封站，就有人屌自己友豬隊友，害隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日無做既話，就算黨鐵封站，大家都只會屌黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafc6f7ee284888fb2c611d0367a6408adff73a3","tid":1528050,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"討論下"},{"pid":"4a4f01f10b92372bdec9da76c976f10bbc06c436","tid":1528050,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1ad